Stay at home
Only go outside for food, health reasons or work (but only if you cannot work from home)
If you go out, stay 2 metres (6ft) away from other people at all times
Wash your hands as soon as you get home
Do not meet others, even friends or family.
You can spread the virus even if you don’t have symptoms.

There are currently no commercial options available to return to the UK from Panama. All commercial flights have now ceased operation to/from Panama until at least 22 May 2020.
Spirit Airlines
Spirit Airlines will be running special flights departing from Panama City, Tocumen International Airport, to Fort Lauderdale, Florida, USA on Friday 15 May and Tuesday 19 May. Passengers with a valid ESTA are qualified for this flight as long as they have been outside one of the designated areas (UK, Republic of Ireland, the Schengen Zone, Iran or China) for more than 14 days. British Nationals who have been outside one of these areas can still apply for an ESTA.
Use the following link to book
There are onward flights to London Heathrow Airport from Miami International Airport. You should coordinate your onward connection to the UK accordingly.
Special European flight
A special European flight, operated by Evelop Air, will depart Panama Tocumen International Airport on Monday 11 May at 2:00pm for Paris, France (CDG). It will make a brief stopover of 1.5hrs in Honduras (San Pedro Sula) to pick up other passengers. Passengers that have boarded the flight in Panama will not be allowed to disembark the plane in Honduras. Arrival to Paris CDG is scheduled for 10:30am Tuesday 12 May.
Registration for the European Evelop Air special flight on 11 May has now closed.
We are not aware of any other special humanitarian flights leaving from Panama City to mainland Europe. There are no plans currently for direct flights to the UK.
This travel advice will be updated with further information on any future special flights and other options to leave Panama as soon as this is available. Please follow the instructions in the ‘If you cannot leave Panama’ section to stay in touch and receive details of further flights.
Transport to the airport
For those with confirmed tickets on this flight. Taxis, Cabify and InDriver continue to operate, as do the two transport options below. Others may be available. You should book in advance and inform us of your arrangements, as below:
Company: Traslados Panama
Contact: Ing. Vladimir Arrocha
